name: P'Chaos | Morgendämmer #XTZ1
description:
🔥 The P'Chaos collection consists of generates of the updated brand new version of Chaos Algorithm. It uses a unique new shader structure in the codebase and adds a sketchy spirit to borders that feels hand drawn.

💀 As a method of P'Chaos, Morgendämmer was coded to depict the cubed particles of planets disintegrating in the vacuum of space. Morgendämmer is a 40-piece P'Chaos sub-collection.

👽 As always, It's all code, just generative art!
